---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Learn about Tarot by the Stars - a free, privacy-focused tarot reading web app with no ads and no data collection."
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-violet-deep text-center">
      About This Site
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading text-violet-medium mb-4">
          What is Tarot?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Tarot is a centuries-old practice of using symbolic cards to gain insight,
          reflect on life's questions, and explore your inner wisdom. Each of the 78 cards
          in a tarot deck carries unique meanings and archetypal energies.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Tarot is a tool for introspection and self-reflection, not prediction.
          The cards help you explore possibilities, gain perspective, and understand
          the energies surrounding your situation.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading text-violet-medium mb-4">
          Our Mission
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Tarot by the Stars was created to provide free, accessible tarot readings
          without the noise of advertisements, paywalls, or data collection. We believe
          spiritual guidance should be available to everyone, privately and freely.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-violet-light bg-opacity-10 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-gold-soft">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-violet-deep mb-2">Our Commitments:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700">
            <li>100% Free - No hidden costs or premium features</li>
            <li>No Ads - Clean, peaceful reading experience</li>
            <li>Privacy First - No data stored on servers, all readings are private</li>
            <li>No Login Required - Start reading immediately</li>
            <li>Open Source - Transparent and community-driven</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading text-violet-medium mb-4">
          The Deck
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          This site uses the traditional Rider-Waite Tarot deck, first published in 1909.
          The imagery and symbolism are now in the public domain, making them freely
          available for study and spiritual practice.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading text-violet-medium mb-4">
          Privacy & Data
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Your readings are completely private. We do not:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <li>Collect or store your reading data on any server</li>
          <li>Track your personal information</li>
          <li>Use cookies for tracking purposes</li>
          <li>Share any data with third parties</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          All reading data is stored locally in your browser's localStorage for your
          convenience. You can clear this at any time through your browser settings.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section id="disclaimer" class="mb-8 bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 p-6 rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading text-violet-deep mb-4">
          ⚠️ Disclaimer
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          <strong>Important:</strong> This site is for entertainment, reflection, and
          spiritual insight only. Tarot readings should not be used as a substitute for
          professional advice.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Always consult qualified professionals for:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-700 mt-2">
          <li>Legal matters - Seek a licensed attorney</li>
          <li>Medical concerns - Consult a healthcare provider</li>
          <li>Financial decisions - Speak with a financial advisor</li>
          <li>Mental health - Contact a licensed therapist or counselor</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="text-center mt-12 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading text-violet-medium mb-4">
          Support This Project
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          If you find value in this free service, consider supporting the project:
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
          <a
            href="https://dangtrinh.site/donation" 
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						target="_blank"
            class="px-6 py-3 bg-gold-soft text-white rounded-lg hover:bg-gold-light transition-colors"
          >
            ☕ Buy Me a Coffee
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/thdang1009/tarotfree"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						target="_blank"
            class="px-6 py-3 border-2 border-violet-medium text-violet-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-violet-medium hover:text-white transition-all"
          >
            ⭐ Star on GitHub
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-12 pt-8 border-t">
        <p>Made with care for the spiritual community</p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          <a href="/" class="text-violet-medium hover:text-gold-soft">← Back to Readings</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
